  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm with my Uncle Martin, who was going to go to Paris.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he's taking me to Paris.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to take a bus through the Russian zone.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after much adventures, which really don't have to go in here, we didn't get to Paris because there were some problems in going to Paris.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we went to a displaced-persons camp, called [NON-ENGLISH], where he rented a-- kind of a condominium.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where I had my bar mitzvah.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an exciting time for me for my bar mitzvah because I could ask them what I could eat.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I requested a big weinerschnitzel with rice, which, to this day, is one of my favorite staples.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was still in Hungary and getting ready to leave.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She left Hungary in the-- in a wheat barge afterwards.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came out to Canada separately.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came out faster.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when my Uncle Martin and Eva, they wanted to go onto Canada, they could not take me because it was going to be too expensive.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they dropped me off at this orphanage, where, incidentally, my wife-- my mother visited me as an aunt because I couldn't tell them that I had a mother because I was there as an orphan.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was the name of this orphanage?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]. .",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the name of the town.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a beautiful place.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From there, they could not get me to Canada because I had scarring on my lungs.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they could get me into the States.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I finally-- through Munich, we, we got a Flying Tiger line, which took us to-- all the way to LaGuardia, stopping off at the Azores, where our engine caught fire.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while the plane was making an emergency landing, I was so-- became so religious.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as soon as we got out of the plane, I ate bacon and eggs, I must admit.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But then we got up again.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we made another crash landing in Saint John's in Newfoundland.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we came in on a tail of a hurricane in LaGuardia, where they took me to the children's home, to the orphanage.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And before they could-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] before they could adopt me, there was a very substantial family came with their Lincoln to adopt me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody got so excited.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said, Schwartz, look.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're getting adopted.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you're going to go to Denver.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Look at the Lincoln they have.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Oh, you're going to have a great time, and everything.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I went to the president of the orphanage.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I said-- I confessed to her that I had a mother, and please, do not send me back to Europe.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She's told me that we are not going to send me back to-- me back to Europe because it's too expensive.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we're going to send you to Toronto to your mother, where she is.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I got to the Union Station in Toronto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I get there with all my baggage.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my family was waiting for me in a big crowd.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My family was substantial at that time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they didn't recognize me because I was so fat.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because in New York they gave me a little card.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They said, it's a refugee boy.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So whenever this little refugee boy went near a hot dog stand, they gave him free hot dogs.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I got into a delicatessen, they gave me free corned beef sandwiches.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became so fat that my family didn't recognize me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to scream at them at the Union Station.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, they looked at me like this, oh, Tom, my god, what happened to you?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is how I met my family again.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the, the-- it was a wonderful reunion.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I lost my weight on one of my first crash diets.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at night, I went to school in Harvard Collegiate.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went from Harvard Collegiate, I went to the University of Toronto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then from the University of Toronto, I went to Hebrew Union College.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And four years before that, I married my wife, Leslie Shore.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have two children.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with-- after Hebrew Union College, we had Ilana at Hebrew Union College.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I went to school there, we were-- we had her at [?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Florida ?] and Fifth with the Lamaze method.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ilana is my daughter, who is now 25.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went for my first cantorial position in Temple Israel in Memphis, Tennessee, where Mark was born.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- for five years, I was in Memphis, Tennessee.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also played racquetball in 1973 with Elvis Presley, OK?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just wanted to tell you that we did that.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, from Memphis, Tennessee, my father-in-law, he invited me back to Toronto to take part in his insurance business.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, at the same time, I was cantor at Temple Emmanuel for 10 years.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I took a sabbatical for a while.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now I'm the cantor of Temple Sinai.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And presently, my children are in Guelph University.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Mark is 22 now.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Ilana is 25.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And thank God I'm here.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's sheer luck I tell you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's luck.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not often.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just talked about the pleasant parts, you know, the onions.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I talked about the, the part when I fell into the honey bin, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just those things, those interesting things.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't talk about the unpleasant things.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, I'm sure it affected me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where hardships don't phase me, hunger doesn't bother me, although I clean my plate all the time.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm-- I'm very appreciative of food because we had so little for such a long time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for a young boy of eight and nine, you know, to have no food is one of the most-- strongest memories in his life.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So therefore, that's why I'm a little heavy [LAUGHS] lately.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure it has.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure it has.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I may have been a little bit tough on Mark, not as tough on Ilana.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always tell them that they have to eat their food.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They can't waste anything.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure-- I'm sure I'm very frugal in many things, not only in material things, but also in mental giving and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] emotional openness.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm frugal.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, but when somebody wants it, I can always give it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it, it-- the, the war has closed me down a lot.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's, I mean, those are the things that I can imagine that have affected me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My, my belief is always the same as it was.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always believe in God.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe that God is a-- is a-- is a-- God is a friendly god, who is a funny god.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's-- He-- He-- He is so big, that He doesn't really know-- He-- He's aware that you're there.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, but you have to help him, you know, so that He can guide you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other words, my imagination of God is, is a little bit different than most people.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To me, God is like a big brother who's always there, not always watching you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In other words, you could actually die.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he'll say, oh, oh, he's dead.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, that's too bad.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's, it's-- to Him, it's nothing, you know, if, if a human being dies.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's because there's so much for Him to-- anyway, that's--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother sustained me a lot.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, the belief in God.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My belief in God was much, much stronger than it is right now.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, it was much more basic.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "God was much more real for me through the camps, and so on.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I, I always thought that people died because they didn't do, do the right thing for God.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even though that they looked innocent, there must have been something there.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I have a very primitive view of God.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that has been modified since then.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is very important to me that people should realize what happened and that we human beings are capable of such despicable and unbelievable cruelty to each other.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want people to know this so that they can guard against this in the future, and that they may be-- they can cure the whole milieu of human beings of these type of feelings that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we are capable of.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think it is possible to do it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yet, maybe in the next two centuries, perhaps it will happen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But until then, you have these atrocities.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, just like in Sarajevo-- and you have it in Rwanda.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people killing each other, like, I mean, it's unbelievable.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, I told you what happens.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After you kill 25 or 50 people, it's already-- it's-- you're used to it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's like nothing.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- that's what we have to be cured of because there's a streak in us that-- that can awaken this unspeakable cruelty.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- this is the thing that I want people to realize and to guard against.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had one nightmare.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not really a nightmare.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a pleasant type of a thing.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- we're running in our cattle cars again.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the cattle car stops.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all come out.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the cattle car changes into a fish-- into a fish.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's-- and then somebody opens the fish.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it's cooked.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's lox.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And somebody yells to get some bagels.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] it's-- that's what it is.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have this occasionally.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it's, it's not a pleasant dream.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's-- I must-- it's a weird dream.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm always scared to death.",
