    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's-- it's hard to believe.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that's what it is.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, is to [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] have-- try and feel what, what the other person feels when you're doing something to him or when you talk to him.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Have empathy.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that's-- I think that's one of the most important things.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do unto others what you-- and others-- [LAUGHS] do not do unto others what you would do badly.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, that's what I want.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Empathize with other people.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once you know how the other people feel-- other person feels-- you can't possibly go wrong.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what we don't do because, because it's very hard to do it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it's a heavy thing to do.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's, it's a lot of work.",
